{
  "page": "Amanda Arryn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Amanda Arryn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Rodrik_Arryn%27s_children_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rodrik Arryn&#39;s children by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Rodrik_Arryn%27s_children_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/350px-Rodrik_Arryn%27s_children_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"/images/6/6d/Rodrik_Arryn%27s_children_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Amanda Arryn (top right) with her sisters Elys and Aemma and two brothers by coldraindropsss ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_62_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">62</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_74_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">74&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Arryn\" title=\"Rodrik Arryn\">Rodrik Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Amanda Arryn</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Amanda_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Amanda was the daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Arryn\" title=\"Rodrik Arryn\">Rodrik Arryn</a> and his first wife. She had three siblings, including an elder sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Elys_Arryn\" title=\"Elys Arryn\">Elys</a>. After her mother died, her father married again to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Daella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Daella Targaryen (daughter of Jaehaerys I)\">Daella Targaryen</a>. Amanda largely wrote letters on behalf of her step-mother to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daella died in childbirth, giving Amanda a younger half-sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Aemma_Arryn\" title=\"Aemma Arryn\">Aemma Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Amanda_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\">